Historical Society--

34:06.957 --> 34:08.307
places that Temperance
would most likely be.

34:08.481 --> 34:10.265
We should check both out.

34:10.352 --> 34:12.267
You in?

34:14.139 --> 34:15.662
Yeah.

34:18.665 --> 34:20.449
[door opens]

34:20.667 --> 34:22.277
[groans softly]

34:27.152 --> 34:28.675
[grunts]

34:38.685 --> 34:40.252
[phone rings]

34:41.688 --> 34:43.124
ACE:
Hey.

34:43.298 --> 34:44.908
Temperance isn't
at the Historical Society,

34:45.126 --> 34:46.171
which means...[Lev yells]

34:46.345 --> 34:47.694
She's here.

34:52.916 --> 34:55.093
[rattling]

34:55.180 --> 34:57.530
[whimpers]

34:57.617 --> 35:00.576
[grunts, screams]

35:00.794 --> 35:02.317
[whimpers, grunts]

35:02.404 --> 35:04.145
Help.

35:06.887 --> 35:10.369
[whimpers][growls]

35:10.586 --> 35:13.459
[grunting loudly]
Help! Help!

35:16.114 --> 35:17.550
[exhales]

35:19.813 --> 35:21.554
[humming "The Battle Hymn
of the Republic"]

35:35.524 --> 35:37.135
[growls]

35:38.962 --> 35:40.877
It may comfort you to know

35:41.051 --> 35:43.880
that I created
a supernatural substance

35:44.054 --> 35:45.752
which you inhaled
and spread through your blood

35:45.926 --> 35:47.580
and into your heart.

35:49.495 --> 35:51.975
That will serve
as my tracking device.

35:52.193 --> 35:54.717
[continues humming]

35:56.023 --> 35:57.851
[gasps]And I will follow

35:58.025 --> 36:00.288
this beast
until he leads me to whomever

36:00.506 --> 36:02.421
holds the fourth piece
of my daughter's soul.

36:02.638 --> 36:04.553
[gasps]

36:08.731 --> 36:10.777
[heart beating]

36:15.042 --> 36:17.784
[Copperhead snarls]

36:28.098 --> 36:30.623
Thank you for your sacrifice.

36:30.710 --> 36:33.408
Know that it was not in vain.PARK:
Lev!

36:34.714 --> 36:36.542
[panting]

36:54.908 --> 36:56.301
[Bess clears throat]

36:56.475 --> 36:58.520
I can't promise you
this won't hurt.

36:58.694 --> 37:00.043
Understood.

37:00.218 --> 37:02.045
Okay.

37:04.047 --> 37:06.354
Hey. Hey, hey, listen.

37:06.572 --> 37:08.487
Listen, nosebleeds
don't last forever, right?

37:08.704 --> 37:10.489
What you need
to be concerned with

37:10.706 --> 37:13.927
are your QB follow-throughs,
right? Hmm?

37:14.144 --> 37:15.494
Fundamentals
are everything.

37:15.711 --> 37:17.278
My follow-throughs
are on point.

37:17.496 --> 37:19.019
I practice
almost every day.

37:19.106 --> 37:20.499
[chuckles softly]

37:20.716 --> 37:21.804
[hissing]

37:26.244 --> 37:29.508
Hey, hey. Here you go.

37:33.512 --> 37:34.948
Your nose stopped bleeding.

37:35.165 --> 37:37.472
Hey, can I... Can I see
the back of your neck?

37:41.520 --> 37:43.043
Hey.

37:55.882 --> 37:57.884
[sighs]

37:59.581 --> 38:01.409
[phone buzzing]

38:06.762 --> 38:08.808
[exhales]

38:08.982 --> 38:11.550
What did you do,
you stupid girl?

38:11.724 --> 38:13.378
Are you gonna let
this stupid girl die

38:13.552 --> 38:15.728
because of a hex
you started?

38:15.815 --> 38:18.687
Don't you need my blood
to open the Veil?

38:40.318 --> 38:43.190
Hmm. Thank you.

38:43.277 --> 38:45.540
Proves that you
really do need me.

38:45.714 --> 38:48.543
So...

38:48.630 --> 38:50.980
come and get me.

39:00.555 --> 39:03.602
Temperance's New Genesis.

39:04.559 --> 39:07.693
♪ I fall through things

39:08.998 --> 39:11.566
♪ Right down to the bottom...

39:12.828 --> 39:14.395
Oh, no.

39:14.613 --> 39:16.397
[roaring] [screaming]

39:16.615 --> 39:18.747
♪

39:18.965 --> 39:21.750
[phone buzzes]

39:23.056 --> 39:24.187
BESS:
Hey.

39:24.405 --> 39:27.321
[sniffles]
Hey. Um...

39:27.495 --> 39:29.541
Is there any chance
you're gonna see Addy tonight?

39:29.715 --> 39:32.282
Hey, what's wrong?
You don't sound okay.

39:32.500 --> 39:33.893
♪ See you through the dark... ♪

39:34.067 --> 39:35.590
It's just, uh...

39:35.764 --> 39:38.071
Um...

39:38.245 --> 39:41.770
I need Addy to take over
the Youth Center.

39:41.944 --> 39:43.903
For-for good.

39:44.077 --> 39:46.253
Nick, no.
Th-Those kids need you.

39:46.427 --> 39:48.255
No, they don't.

39:48.342 --> 39:49.691
I kept the hexes a secret

39:49.865 --> 39:53.042
when I should have
told you all sooner.

39:53.129 --> 39:55.088
I chose the wrong ritual.

39:55.262 --> 39:57.003
I keep breaking my promises.

39:57.220 --> 39:59.832
To the kids. To...

39:59.919 --> 40:01.747
To George.

40:03.226 --> 40:05.751
Her sisters.

40:05.925 --> 40:09.668
I told George that no matter
what tries to get in our way,

40:09.885 --> 40:11.060
I would never say goodbye
to her.

40:11.234 --> 40:14.150
In this life or the next.

40:14.324 --> 40:17.153
But everything's
falling apart, Bess.

40:17.327 --> 40:19.286
♪ You'll keep on taking... ♪

40:19.460 --> 40:21.244
[crying]

40:21.419 --> 40:23.943
I can't...

40:24.117 --> 40:26.511
I can't do it anymore.

40:26.685 --> 40:28.469
♪ You swore you'd hidden... ♪

40:28.643 --> 40:30.602
[sniffles]

40:32.908 --> 40:35.084
It's time I rethink everything.

40:40.699 --> 40:42.309
[phone buzzes]

40:42.483 --> 40:43.876
Nick?PARK:
Bess. Hey.

40:44.050 --> 40:45.747
Oh. Agent Park.

40:45.921 --> 40:49.577
Listen, did an excellent job
profiling Temperance.

40:49.795 --> 40:51.492
I was hoping
you could help me locate her

40:51.666 --> 40:54.103
now that I've received
some new evidence.

40:54.190 --> 40:55.888
What kind of evidence?

40:55.975 --> 40:57.672
Lev, unfortunately.

40:57.759 --> 40:59.674
I found his body.Oh, God.

40:59.848 --> 41:01.676
Poor Lev.

41:01.763 --> 41:03.983
The Copperhead killed him
in Stratemeyer Woods.

41:04.157 --> 41:06.942
Uh, s-so,
the Copperhead killed him?

41:07.160 --> 41:08.857
Not Temperance?

41:09.075 --> 41:11.338
Looks that way.

41:11.425 --> 41:13.166
And Lev's death
will have triggered

41:13.383 --> 41:15.124
the final victim's dreams,

41:15.211 --> 41:17.823
just like Matthew Burke's death
prompted Jake Cazine's dreams

41:18.040 --> 41:20.173
and Jake Cazine's death
set off Lev's dreams.

41:20.347 --> 41:22.044
So, somewhere out there,

41:22.218 --> 41:24.177
the-the person containing
the last piece of Charity's soul

41:24.351 --> 41:26.353
is having a dream
about Gettysburg.

41:26.440 --> 41:28.616
[indistinct shouting] Whoever this last person is,

41:28.834 --> 41:31.140
we don't have much time
to find them.

41:31.227 --> 41:35.057
♪ Only time will tell ♪

41:37.538 --> 41:39.540
[artillery firing]

41:41.107 --> 41:42.935
[panting]

41:43.109 --> 41:45.154
[heart pounding]

